{"tid":2308284,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【懷舊】有冇人好懷念Asiadog年代嘅game？","createTime":"2020-12-01T18:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T17:58:10.000Z","uid":68916,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fab336d2ca8d8bd7da6789a6a10f0aa9e2d4e652","tid":2308284,"uid":68916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:29:57.000Z","msg":"抄下post先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好多都好正，唔同類型都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />btw發現而家好多都玩唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求其講啲<br />\n足球嗰啲，碧咸3D罰球好鬼正，細個成日瘋狂拉西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Euro 2004個桌上game又係正（兩隻都玩唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n賽車嗰堆又係，有個香口膠會痴住部車嗰個3D賽車又係好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n智力嗰度，碌木跌入窿嗰個好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過河遊戲又係，次次玩返都搞勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有DNA同無個性戰隊呢啲唔洗講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e56dcb84754c03876e2692839f4ef32e7ca1c5","tid":2308284,"uid":278392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:33:06.000Z","msg":"有香口膠個隻賽車我都記得，想玩翻<br />\n叫咩名？"},{"pid":"8e7d22efabf70e88876f95cceb33b7bfad8b6676","tid":2308284,"uid":41826,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:33:28.000Z","msg":"細個成日偷偷地玩入面啲咸game<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bcfedd585e3c1e14adc58f296eb03b74da3034","tid":2308284,"uid":141022,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T18:33:58.000Z","msg":"淨係會玩限制級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb43ec9a0e50ff308ffc931